data.description: Beautiful custom brick & cedar 2 story home situated on oversized lot! This home is immaculate and has been well maintained by the second owner. New 2021 remodeled kitchen features espresso cabinets, new backsplash, new countertops, huge island with seating, new appliances, and pantry. Enjoy the sun-soaked formal living room with bay window that flows effortlessly into the formal dining room. Highly sought after open floor plan from kitchen to the 14x24 family room complete with vaulted ceiling & convenient gas fireplace. First floor also features powder room and convenient mudroom with laundry. All 3 bedrooms upstairs ~ Large primary suite complete with en suite bathroom, skylight, and walk-in closet. Basement is ready for your finishing touches and perfect for storage right now! 2.5 Car attached garage and a 6 car driveway! Other updates/features: Garage door (2019), roof (2013), high efficiency furnace (2023), new sump pumps (2021), new patio. Lake park school district & great location near downtown Roselle, shopping, Metra train, Starbucks, expressways and dog park!
